data.description: This beautiful 3 bed/2 bath home is located right in the heart of Bryant, just 2 blocks from Mills Park & walking distance to Bryant Schools!  The home features 2 large living areas - one w a dining combo and the other with a large fireplace.  Covered back patio and spacious back yard for entertaining.  ***AGENTS SEE REMARKS!!!***
